      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "An unnamed person called police in Michigan to report their car had been stolen. Like we’ve said, this happens way too often and usually the outcome is filing an insurance claim, hopefully getting most of the loan paid for that way, and then buying a new car. However, this time the person not only had a ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
